Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.92,0:02:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反覆思考之後 蕾孤身前往煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.29,0:02:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追趕她的酷等人與煌珠獵人臥魯克斯再次相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.39,0:02:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到他只把搭檔吉露露當作工具使喚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.31,0:02:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷再次被激怒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.16,0:02:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是吉露露卻\N奮不顧身地保護對她惡言相向的臥魯克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠與同契者的關係真是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深深銘刻在內心深處之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.53,0:02:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷等人繼續啟程去追趕蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵循命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.37,0:02:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經在艾波赫利大陸\N建起了我們ChaosChoir的前線基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.96,0:02:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在增援到來之前保護好基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 不准向任何人洩漏我們的真實身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果附近出現可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要把他們幹掉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.11,0:03:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已在數日前擊退了進犯的守護翼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊退？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.93,0:03:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確定他們斷氣了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這 這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.59,0:03:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.23,0:03:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可愛的玩偶 我是不喜歡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是不允許再次失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個基地必須好好守住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是連這也做不到的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.60,0:03:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你們想成為真正的煌珠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.73,0:03:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十五唱 大風車的村莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.89,0:05:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.02,0:05:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由靳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧麗佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.06,0:05:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把飛機...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先放著好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡作劇也要適可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是不乖乖聽我們的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次就讓你吃點苦頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就來試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.61,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會打破這堵牆讓風車再次轉起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.84,0:05:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在這種地方耽擱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點找蕾的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 在那之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想去這城市的醫院看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去醫院幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個以前照顧過我們的守護翼的前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說在幾天前受了重傷住院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你們就去看望他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在就要去找蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這兒讓我下車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.46,0:06:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙威魯德前輩是為執行特別任務而被派遣到這地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.92,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定他知道一些盯上蕾的敵人的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得有點不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但害你嚇了一跳還要讓你幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然一個人站在那種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣下去的話是轉不起來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.01,0:06:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.87,0:06:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那座風車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要沒有那堵石牆的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.69,0:06:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在幾個月前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的那幫流氓襲擊了村莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強迫我們造了那堵石牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.83,0:07:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村裏的人雖然在一開始也有過抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙總在關鍵時刻使用奇怪的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.95,0:07:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以打不過他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.83,0:07:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後大家都聽他們的擺佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是用那風車抽取地下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.89,0:07:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸送到村裏及田里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但自從有了那堵牆之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風的通路就被擋住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田地完全乾枯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連日常飲用水也供應困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以一定要破壞那堵牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.76,0:07:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.34,0:07:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方的建築物\N都是以頂上的五角形拱心石為中心建造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.34,0:07:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要破壞了那裏整堵牆就會倒塌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而那堵石牆也是用相同的方法建造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 只要坐著這東西飛到那附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.81,0:07:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞了那塊石頭的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這飛機是由靳做的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由靳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又去胡鬧了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我適可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是你亂弄一氣惹得他們來報復怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光等著風是不會吹過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不通過自己的力量讓風車轉起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正沒用的 放棄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了忍耐沒其他辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒那回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但願沙威魯德前輩的傷勢好轉 能跟我們說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀 是希絲卡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.74,0:08:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.58,0:08:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在這裏見到姐姐 夏爾羅真是太高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和龍也好多年不見了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 別站在門口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.98,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快進來 快進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you 幫了大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.74,0:09:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓蕾住在我家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.90,0:09:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.15,0:09:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.26,0:09:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來 得趕緊把這東西修好才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天一定要破壞那堵牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.68,0:09:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.55,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 對了 飯做好後就給你送來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是這樣 謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來 請吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到你身體安康 我暫且放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.82,0:09:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩居然受這麼重的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 是這樣的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說最近在這地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.53,0:09:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個神秘組織在對抗守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就去調查它的底細
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查之後 發現了一處疑為敵人前線基地的設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛入探個究竟時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遭到敵人伏擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.83,0:10:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同契之後很快就被打得落花流水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是千鈞一髮之際
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但總算是逃了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 那個敵人的組織的名字是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.88,0:10:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 組織的名字好像是叫ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前曾有個自稱是ChaosChoir的特工的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.41,0:10:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,襲擊過酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.86,0:10:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是說要抓蕾的人正在這附近轉悠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在想 他是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他叫酷德·望·朱魯愛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是七煌寶樹的同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誒 是他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.39,0:10:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我們也得告辭了 得馬上去追他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了 龍威 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.29,0:11:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於ChaosChoir這個敵人還是再多瞭解一些為好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要出事啊 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很魯莽吧 由靳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.00,0:11:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那麼小的飛機想要轉動那麼大的風車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.58,0:11:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.33,0:11:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.44,0:11:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但錯的事他絕對不會去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.36,0:12:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾也認識這樣的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.02,0:12:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想轉動那個風車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風車就交給你了 奧麗佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.15,0:12:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.83,0:13:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.92,0:15:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.90,0:17:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.44,0:17:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為...和我在一起的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想那麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定就算那樣也要和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想那麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.22,0:17:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.04,0:17:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏的是從天使守護隊總部逃出來的七煌寶樹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也是煌珠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.71,0:17:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是ChaosChoir的擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是來救我們的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點和我們同契吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那些傢伙幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救你們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只不過是需要你們的身體而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.88,0:18:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於我們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.93,0:18:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有比抓住七煌寶樹更重要的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快點離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.68,0:18:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.62,0:18:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幽美星夜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.77,0:18:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牽引之線{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼此傾心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追及之畏{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.62,0:18:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深藏在心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與我共頌念{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,締結契約{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣息相應{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纏繞飛旋之風{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝與我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠相隨{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤誠之心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纏繞飛揚之風{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,締結契約{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛藏於暗夜之中{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所侍奉之青龍{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心之澄境蘊風雲{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漩風飛速聚集{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.13,0:19:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黎明前之朦月{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝與我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心意互通{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南風之弦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.49,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是沙威魯德前輩所說的ChaosChoir的擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.21,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是前所未有的可怕的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.59,0:19:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來幹得真漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.14,0:19:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來他們潛藏著超乎我們想像的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.20,0:20:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得越來越注意他們兩個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.16,0:20:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.98,0:20:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上保重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.21,0:20:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說呢 那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再亂跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從今往後我們永遠一起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得太好了 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 我們已經是命運共同體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.21,0:21:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論前面有著多麼嚴酷的考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.29,0:21:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天涯海角我們都攜手共行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.62,0:22:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人在理想與現實的夾縫中生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.16,0:22:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論想選擇哪一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰都無法阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.87,0:22:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回 追憶的子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伴隨著槍聲響起 少女失去了溫情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.87,0:23:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十六唱 追憶的子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.52,0:13:33.01,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,たとえばここには愛すべき声があって{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.70,0:13:39.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,あたしはそれすら守らなくて{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.14,0:13:48.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五月雨　街を照らす黄昏{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.28,0:13:56.94,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,そう　隠した思い出に染まってる{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.99,0:14:01.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,さよならだなんて夢ならいいって{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晴れない心模様{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.18,0:14:09.79,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨ならやむってニュースが言ってる{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,もう　行かなくちゃ{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:38.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大事な事ほど目に映らない法則{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.31,0:14:45.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,あたしは今さら悔いたりして{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.81,0:14:54.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,色彩　移り行く紫陽花{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.86,0:15:02.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,まだ　記憶を憂鬱になぞってる{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:07.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,あどけないままのあの日の愛を{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.21,0:15:10.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘れていいのかな{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.87,0:15:15.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頬濡らす雫　乾いてゆく{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ほら行かなくちゃ{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.98,0:15:50.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,言葉を越えたつもりでいた{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.25,0:15:53.29,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,あれは夢だった？{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.94,0:15:58.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慣れた体温を探してないよ{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,もう行けるでしょう？{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.04,0:16:06.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,さよならだなんて夢ならいいって{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晴れない心模様{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.27,0:16:14.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ふと飛び越えた水たまりに{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.90,0:16:18.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ほら　空の色{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.76,0:16:27.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,たとえばここには愛すべき声があって{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.95,0:16:34.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,あたしはそれすら守らなくて{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.52,0:13:33.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,或許 這裏有戀人的聲音{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.70,0:13:39.73,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,而我 卻連那也守護不了{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.14,0:13:48.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,梅雨中 夕陽照耀著街道{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.28,0:13:56.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,浸染那深藏於心的回憶{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.99,0:14:01.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,「分手只是一場夢該多好」{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,愁緒無法釋懷{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.18,0:14:09.79,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,預報說雨快停了{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,好了 該出發了{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:38.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,越重要的東西 卻越無法映入眼簾{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.31,0:14:45.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,我 現在才開始後悔{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.81,0:14:54.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,花色漸變的紫陽花{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.86,0:15:02.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,記憶仍帶著憂鬱的痕跡{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:07.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,天真爛漫的昔日之愛{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.21,0:15:10.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,是否可以忘記{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.87,0:15:15.40,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,臉頰上的水滴 已逐漸干去{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.64,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,嗯 該出發了{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.98,0:15:50.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,曾感到你我之間無需言語{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.25,0:15:53.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,那只是南柯一夢嗎？{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.94,0:15:58.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,我已不再探尋你那熟悉的體溫{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,已經 可以離去了吧{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.04,0:16:06.68,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,「分手只是一場夢該多好」{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.70,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,愁緒無法釋懷{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.27,0:16:14.84,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,不經意間躍過的水坑中{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.90,0:16:18.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,看 倒映著天空的顏色{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.76,0:16:27.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,或許 這裏有戀人的聲音{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.95,0:16:34.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,!Effect,而我 卻連那也守護不了{\an9}

